diseases.title: Diseases
diseases.description: The disease, disorder, syndrome, illness, or injury that is being studied. On ClinicalTrials.gov, conditions may also include other health-related issues, such as lifespan, quality of life, and health risks.

interventions.title: Interventions
interventions.description: A process or action that is the focus of a clinical study. Interventions include drugs, medical devices, procedures, vaccines, and other products that are either investigational or already available. Interventions can also include noninvasive approaches, such as education or modifying diet and exercise.

nctid.title: Nctid
nctid.description: NCT ID of the clinical trial study

locations.title: Locations
locations.description: Name of the country or city

OPERATOR.title: Operator
OPERATOR.description: Enable detect before and after the year
